boardgame-go
Copyright (c) 2026 Tyler Crandall

This project is a Go port modeled on the API surface and conceptual design
of boardgame.io (https://github.com/boardgameio/boardgame.io). No source
code from boardgame.io is included in this repository; the Go
implementation is freshly authored. However, the public types, field
names, and overall game-definition shape (Game, Setup, Moves, Phases,
Turn, EndIf, etc.) deliberately mirror the upstream project so that game
logic can be translated between the two with mechanical changes.

